Available Tools: send_sms | send_bulk_sms | get_sms_status | get_sms_history
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "to": "string", "message": "string", "from": "string" }
Response Schema: { "message_id": "string", "to": "string", "status": "string", "cost": number, "timestamp": "string" }
---
Question: Send a welcome message to a new subscriber in Rome.
Call: { "func_call": "send_sms", "to": "+390612345678", "message": "Welcome to ItaliaNews! Reply STOP to unsubscribe.", "from": "ItaliaNews" }
Response: { "message_id": "msg_it_7729384", "to": "+390612345678", "status": "sent", "cost": 0.055, "timestamp": "2023-11-15T09:12:30Z" }

Question: Alert all members of a gym chain in Madrid about pool maintenance.
Call: { "func_call": "send_bulk_sms", "to": "+34912345678,+34912345679,+34912345680", "message": "Notice: Main pool closed for cleaning until 5 PM today.", "from": "FitES" }
Response: { "message_id": "bulk_es_4421093", "to": "+34912345678,+34912345679,+34912345680", "status": "processing", "cost": 0.031, "timestamp": "2023-11-15T09:15:45Z" }

Question: Verify if a flight update was delivered to a passenger in Amsterdam.
Call: { "func_call": "get_sms_status", "to": "+31612345678", "message": "STATUS_CHECK", "from": "SkyNL" }
Response: { "message_id": "msg_nl_9912304", "to": "+31612345678", "status": "delivered", "cost": 0.049, "timestamp": "2023-11-15T09:18:22Z" }

Question: Pull the history of all survey invitations sent from the Oslo campaign.
Call: { "func_call": "get_sms_history", "to": "campaign_oslo_winter", "message": "HISTORY_REQUEST", "from": "SurveyNO" }
Response: { "message_id": "hist_no_3320194", "to": "campaign_oslo_winter", "status": "retrieved", "cost": 0.00, "timestamp": "2023-11-15T09:20:10Z" }

